The paper deals with a wireless network cooperation model and derives analytic expressions based on stochastic geometry for the coverage probability in the network. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Machine Learning (cs.MA), and Game Theory (cs.GT) sub-categories.
